9.  That the exhibitor further undertakes to pay over above share if any immediately after its termination/discontinuation of the films.
10. That publicity expenses if any will be borne by the exhibitor alone and shall not be deducted in the DCR OR Share.
11. Parties agree that this Agreement and all disputes, claims and differences arising out of and under this Agreement shall in all respects, be subject to and submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts in Hubballi and no other courts.
12. Rest of the terms shall be as practiced in the film trade.


